xtgk is a demo of a separately compiled and install plugin for graphviz.

To build from CVS, use:

	cd xgtk
	./autogen.sh 
	make
	make install

To make a distributable version, use:

	cd xgtk
	./autogen.sh
	make dist
	

	zcat xgtk-plugin-0.1tar.gz | tar xf -
	cd xgtk-plugin-0.1
	./configure 
	make 
	make install


To make an rpm:

	cd xgtk
	./autogen.sh
	make rpm

